<h2>You've been invited to participate in "<%= @ballot.name %>"</h2>

<p><%= @inviter_email %> has invited you to participate in a vote using Voqua's quadratic voting system.</p>

<p>With quadratic voting, you'll receive voting credits to allocate across different options. This allows you to express not just your preferences, but also how strongly you feel about each choice.</p>

<%= link_to 'Join Vote', @url, class: 'button' %>
